Package com.esri.mo2.data.spx

Classes that provide an in-memory spatial index.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
MutableTree This interface defines a mutable tree of spatial objects.
NodeVisitor Defines a Visitor for searching or traversing a Tree.
Tree This interface defines a tree that can be used to manage objects spatially.
 

Class Summary
BaseMutableTree A default implementation of the MutableTree interface.
BaseTree A default implementation of the Tree interface.
SpatialNode A base object for all objects to be placed in the spatial tree.
